title: Top 10 novels(ebooks) of 2014 - [pdf+epub+mobi] - [HeadbangersFC
description:
Hello folks, this is my list of best novels of 2014. Some good ones might be missing and you won't agree, so please understand that I can fit only 10 in this list. This is the top 10 list according to me, in the year 2014. ENJOY READING!


Top 10 books are:-

All the Light We Cannot See - Anthony Doerr

Boy, Snow, Bird - Helen Oyeyemi

Can't and Won't - Lydia Davis

Dept. Of Speculation - Jenny Offill

Every Day Is for the Thief - Teju Cole

Everything I Never Told You - Celeste NG

Leaving the Sea - Ben Marcus

The Shock of the Fall (Special edition) - Nathan Filer

The Silkworm - Robert Galbraith

To Rise Again at a Decent Hour - Joshua Ferris


PLEASE SEED AND SHARE. THANK YOU.


Format - epub,pdf, mobi
